rounds.event: Air Indiana Flight 216 crashes near Evansville Regional Airport, killing 29, including the University of Evansville basketball team, support staff, and boosters of the team.
deaths: Oguz Atay, Turkish engineer and author

rounds.event: The 6.0 North Yemen earthquake shakes southwestern Yemen with a maximum Mercalli intensity of VIII (Severe), killing 2,800, and injuring 1,500.
births: Dan Hamhuis, Canadian ice hockey player
